# Privacy Policy for B Notes - Simple Note Taking App

At B Notes, we prioritize the privacy of our users. This Privacy Policy document outlines the types of information collected and recorded by B Notes - Simple Note Taking App and how we use it.

If you have any questions or need further information about our Privacy Policy, please don't hesitate to contact us.

## Information Collection and Usage

### User-Provided Information

B Notes may collect personal information such as your name and email address when you voluntarily submit it within the app, for purposes such as creating an account or contacting support. We may use this information to respond to your inquiries, provide user support, or notify you about important changes to the app.

### Automatically Collected Information

Like many other apps, B Notes may automatically collect non-personal information when you use the app. This may include but is not limited to device information, device type, operating system, app usage data, and crash reports. This information is used for analyzing trends, improving app performance, and enhancing the user experience.

## Data Security

We are committed to protecting your data and ensuring its security. While we take reasonable precautions to safeguard your personal information, no method of data transmission over the internet or electronic storage is completely secure. Therefore, we cannot guarantee the absolute security of your data.

## Third-Party Services

B Notes may use third-party services, such as cloud storage providers, to enhance the functionality of the app. Please be aware that these third-party services may have their own privacy policies and terms of service. We recommend reviewing their policies to understand how your data is handled when using their services in conjunction with B Notes.

## Children's Privacy

B Notes is not intended for children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children. If you are a parent or guardian and believe that your child has provided us with personal information, please contact us, and we will take steps to remove that information from our records.

## Changes to Privacy Policy

B Notes may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify users of any changes by posting the updated Privacy Policy within the app. By continuing to use the app after such changes are made, you consent to the revised Privacy Policy.

## Contact Us

If you have any questions, concerns, or requests regarding this Privacy Policy or your personal data, please contact us at [contact@bnotesapp.com](mailto:contact@bnotesapp.com).

By using B Notes - Simple Note Taking App, you agree to the terms and conditions outlined in this Privacy Policy.
